title: New PlayStation IP from Jade Raymond's New Studio - Kinda Funny Games Daily 03.16.21
description:
IT'S A WEIRD WHITTA-LESS (NON)WEDNESDAY EPISODE. Greg and Bless talk about Jade Raymond's PlayStation game, Fortnite's changes, and a giant mole. IT'S WEIRD.

Time Stamps - 
00:00:00 - Start
00:10:00 - Housekeeping
There’s a new PSILY live RIGHT NOW!
My spoiler-free Snyder Cut Review
The Kinda Funny Wild Aces are in the FCF Championship. Come call the plays as we take on the Glacier boys this Saturday on twitch.tv/kindafunnygames at 5 pm PT!
Thank you to our Patreon Producers: Mick @DaNanoBiologist Abrahamson, Black Jack, & Trent Berrie
The Roper Report   -
00:12:00 - Jade Raymond Starts a Studio, Making a PlayStation IP!
